{"tid":1702102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【人間記者會】高松傑所屬音樂學校光速割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T14:02:25.000Z","uid":93536,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"db0fb1ed1fba30737ff0e4e8891cdf9c925f4df6","tid":1702102,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">老鼠牙任職音樂堂市場及亞洲業務總監，開完人間記者會就比自己間公司光速割蓆</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PkJTXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PkJTXq.jpg&h=2d1ce562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係音樂堂老闆（圖右）同老鼠牙係表兄弟</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xb1FDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xb1FDn.jpg&h=1e6be51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">音樂堂本身亦都藍到仆街，仲送小朋友返大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/09/215050_0190dfc52ad270f6900716e08064615b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F09%2F215050_0190dfc52ad270f6900716e08064615b.png&h=b8cec75e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50ySNj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50ySNj1.png&h=58c914ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無理由割個蓆就置身事外架嘛，起碼貼張五大訴求缺一不可出黎睇睇先啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c9fdce00ac7d90a2403d87564e3a1f53b53998","tid":1702102,"uid":93536,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qtcwit4.jp